Aman Gupta joined Barclays in April 2025. He holds both a Bachelor’s and a Master’s degree in Statistics from the University of Delhi. Prior to Barclays, Aman worked at ZS Associates and Turing, where he gained diverse experience in Data Science and Generative AI, contributing to a wide range of machine learning and GenAI projects. He is proficient in Python, skilled in Prompt Engineering for effectively leveraging GenAI models, and has hands-on experience in data analysis and building interactive presentation portals. Passionate about data science, Aman is eager to continue learning, exploring innovative solutions, and growing with the team.
